KP Building Products Inc. Key Developments

KP Building Products Invests $3.2 Million in its Farley Window and Patio Door Division
Apr 25 17
KP Building Products announced a $3.2 million investment in its Farley Brand of Window and Patio door manufacturing facility. The investment includes a painting facility as well as additional manufacturing equipment to its window operation in order to meet the increased demand for Farley branded PVC windows and doors.


